Hi friends =F0=9F=91=8B,
Happy Friday and welcome back to our 115th Weekly Dose of Optimism. It was =
another scary weather week down in the Southeast and we hope all of our rea=
ders in the impacted zones are safe and secure. I think it=E2=80=99s pretty=
 safe, at this point, to say that this extreme weather is caused in part by=
 climate change. We=E2=80=99re not going to get in the mud on what causes c=
limate change or propose political solutions for addressing it, but we are =
optimistic that there are technologist and researchers working on solutions=
 right now that will mitigate both the causes and effects of climate change=
 in the future.
Let=E2=80=99s get to it.
